    "The AI model predicts the adaptability given in blue-shaded (target) and red-shaded (AI-predicted) spheres.",
    "The radius is scaled according to the adaptability value.",
    "The model can correctly identify the rigid residues (small spheres) but also the amino acids with high flexibility.",
